tune dekhi hai wo peshani wo rukhsar wo hont ....
zindagi jinke tasawwur me luta di hamne ....
tujhpe utthhi hai wo khoi hui saahir aankhen  ...
zindagi jinke taqaddus me ganwa di hamne 

baroz-e-hashr bina khauf ghus jaunga janat me ...
wahan se aaye the aadam wo mere baap ka ghar hai 


-------------jawab-e-shikwa-----------------

in amaal k sath jannat ka talabgaar hai kya..
wahan se nikaale gye aadam to teri auqaat hai kya?

